pan><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">c</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
